 soon. Do you folks know of any similarly rewarding quests? I have no weapon preferences - in fact, I'd be happy to get a variety of weapon types so that I can keep my skills in shape (I'm using 2HS and 1HS atm).<br><br><br>[ Benek ]<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uracketwarborn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RacketWarborn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/6/02 12:06:09 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=435.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Easy Quests Rewarding Weapons?</span><hr size=1> As a 49 Cleric, you can easily get a group in Karnors where you have a chance of <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=745">this weapon</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> dropping. That and a Centi Longsword would be a good combo... Being a cleric you can make cash easily to buy the longsword. <p><center><img src="http://www.geocities.com/racketeq/sig2.txt"><p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=141053">*Racket, Warlord of Valoran*</a><p>--Karana--</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uketelkaotic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ketel Kaotic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/6/02 3:30:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=435.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.blizzard.com/images/broodwar/popup/lurker.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Easy Quests Rewarding Weapons?</span><hr size=1> yep centi long sword is nice sells fairly cheap like 1-2k on quellious<br><br>Dont know many quests for weapons.... there is always the Lansaex <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p><center><img src="http://www.ketelkaotic.com/newsig.jpg"><br><a href="http://www.wraithguild.com">Wraith Guild</a><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=198188"> My Profile</a><br></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uketelkaotic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ketel Kaotic</A> at: 5/6/02 11:20:21 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/usplaktar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Splaktar</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_greenspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 226<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/6/02 10:55:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=435.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Easy Quests Rewarding Weapons?</span><hr size=1> Warriors don't really have decent quests, like casting classes do.  Just grab a junk weapon from OS, Luclin, KC, etc, with your cleric, and it'll be just fine. <p><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=55265">Splack 60 High Priest</a><BR><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=55273">Gurgel 60 Warlord</a><BR><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=55268">Samas 54 Heretic</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ucomparisonjones.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Comparison Jones</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 124<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/7/02 8:48:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=435.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.nimueserver.com/images/personal/comp_head.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Easy Quests Rewarding Weapons?</span><hr size=1> Heh, get 2 more levels den hit Sebilis...  Wif all da gems dat yoo will get der (most groups give all da gems to da cleric by default) yoo can afford some nice gear pretty quick... dat n' yoo can pickup a Lamentation der too, which is IMO pretty nice fer lower level warriors... <p><center><img src=http://www.nimueserver.com/images/personal/cj_tiny.jpg height=143 width=362 border=0><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=176133" target="_blank"><font size="2">My Profile</font></a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ubenekbertoxx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Benek Bertoxx</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/7/02 9:58:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=435.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Easy Quests Rewarding Weapons?</span><hr size=1> Well... as I said, I'm poor atm, so I would really prefer to equip my Warrior with weapons which I get from quests, instead of ones which I need to buy.<br><br>As for looting gems in OS - I believe in equal share. I think that when the group is done, the Cleric (Enchanter too maybe, for skins... *shrug*) should get gems worth the value of peridots I spend in the group, and the rest of the cash loot (which should be way more than the fraction I got) should be equally distributed among all group members.<br><br>Of course, most king-looters rip you off (or at least try to), telling you that they gave all the gems to the Cleric, who only got a 15pp gem, and the rest all stay in the king-looter's pocket. People like me pay attention to what getst distributed though. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br><br>Anyway... I guess if there really aren't any other doable quests which rewards decent weapons (sorry, Langseax doesn't qualify as that anymore, hehe <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ) I'll equip my Warrior with the weapons I win in groups. I hope someone still pops up with some quest though!<br><br>[ Benek ] <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ubenekbertoxx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Benek Bertoxx</A> at: 5/7/02 10:00:15 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uracketwarborn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RacketWarborn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/8/02 2:45:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=435.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Easy Quests Rewarding Weapons?</span><hr size=1> Sad, but true... There are no weapon quests for warriors that I would USE the reward at the level I could do the quest. <p><center><img src="http://www.geocities.com/racketeq/sig2.txt"><p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=141053">*Racket, Warlord of Valoran*</a><p>--Karana--</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uwazazaabi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Waza Zaabi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/8/02 6:37:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=435.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Easy Quests Rewarding Weapons?</span><hr size=1> You can get an onyxbrand in Crystal Caverns for 50pp <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=6045">everquest.allakhazam.com/...?item=6045</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>I did it with a pickup group. This is part of a bigger quest &quot;the spirit of garzicor&quot;<br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=1277">everquest.allakhazam.com/...quest=1277</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>Hope it helps<br><br>Waza<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/unjialstormcaller.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Njial Stormcaller</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 176<br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/8/02 8:07:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=435.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Easy Quests Rewarding Weapons?</span><hr size=1> haha spirit quest is anything but easy, and the weapon isnt all that great to boot. <p><center><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=46665